data.meta_description: Monument – Victoria Memorial, Kolkata Built by – Conceptualised by Lord Curzon Built in – 1906-1921 The Victoria Memorial Hall is a veritable city icon, representing the Indo-Saracenic revivalist style of Architecture. one of the most magnificent monuments, Not only of the city of Kolkata but of the entire country. data.text:
THE HERITAGE ART

India – is a land of myriad and exquisite cultures and traditions. An ancient civilization with roots stretching back to millennials ago. The cradle of the human race, we pay ode to our motherland India.

The Heritage Art is a curated Indian Souvenirs Shop founded with a mission of 'GharGharHeritage' - delivering at least one MADE IN INDIA souvenir in every Indian household.

We are transforming what it means to be heritage-inspired collectible souvenirs and lifestyle gifts. Every keepsake we offer – today and tomorrow - is crafted with our love for heritage, passion for its remembrance and concern for its future. Because every landmark and monument deserves to be immortalised in the pages of our history.

Get in touch with us to empower local artisans and preserve traditional art forms through our curated range of heritage-inspired souvenirs. Feel free to drop us a line here.
